---

<BaseLayout
  title="Canada Certificate Attestation in UAE | Index Office & Services"
  description="Canada certificate attestation in UAE by Index Office with 25+ years of experience in Embassy legalization and MOFA approval. Call us now!"
>

<style>
  .sec-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .idx-pill { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.28); color: #fff; font-size: 0.78rem; padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 9999px; font-weight: 500; white-space: nowrap; }
  .step-card { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #eef0f6; border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px; transition: all 0.25s; }
  .step-card:hover { border-color: #B2F5EA; box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(56,178,172,0.08); }
  .benefit-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px; }
  .faq-item { border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
  .faq-q { width: 100%; background: #fff; border: none; text-align: left; padding: 18px 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: #1A202C; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .faq-a { padding: 0 20px; max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.35s ease, padding 0.2s; }
  .faq-a.open { max-height: 240px; padding: 0 20px 16px; }
  .faq-icon { font-size: 1.1rem; transition: transform 0.3s; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .faq-item.open .faq-icon { transform: rotate(45deg); }

  .split-grid { display: grid !important; }
  .three-col { display: grid !important; }
  .two-col { display: grid !important; }
  .get-started-grid { display: grid !important; }

  @media(max-width:768px){
    .hero-title { font-size: 2rem !important; }
    .split-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 32px !important; }
    .three-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    .get-started-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
  }
</style>

<!-- ════════════ HERO ════════════ -->
<section style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;min-height:500px;display:flex;align-items:center;">
  <img
    src="/images/img-103.webp"
    alt="Canada Certificate Attestation in the UAE"
    style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center 40%;display:block;"
  />
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(26,32,44,0.92) 0%,rgba(45,55,72,0.80) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:radial-gradient(rgba(56,178,172,0.18) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:28px 28px;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;"></div>

  <div class="sec-inner" style="max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;padding:96px 24px;text-align:center;width:100%;">
    <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:18px;">
      <span class="idx-pill">Canada Attestation</span>
      <span class="idx-pill">25 Years of Trust</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-title" style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3.2rem);font-weight:900;color:#fff;line-height:1.15;margin:0 0 20px;">
      CANADA CERTIFICATE ATTESTATION<br/>IN THE UAE
    </h1>
    <p style="color:#B2F5EA;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.8;margin:0 auto 32px;max-width:660px;">
      Canada certificate attestation is required when documents issued in Canada need legal acceptance in the UAE. With 25+ years of experience, IndexAUH follows the correct embassy and MOFA steps to complete attestation without delays.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="#get-in-touch" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#38B2AC;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;padding:13px 28px;border-radius:9999px;text-decoration:none;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(56,178,172,0.4);">Get Free Consultation &rarr;</a>
      <a href="#details" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);color:#fff;font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem;padding:13px 28px;border-radius:9999px;text-decoration:none;">Learn More</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ════ OVERVIEW ════ -->
<section id="details" style="background:#fff;padding:76px 24px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:repeating-linear-gradient(135deg,transparent,transparent 48px,rgba(56,178,172,0.04) 48px,rgba(56,178,172,0.04) 49px);pointer-events:none;z-index:0;"></div>

  <div class="sec-inner split-grid" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.2fr 1fr;gap:52px;align-items:center;">
    <div>
      <p style="color:#2D3748;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:0.75rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:12px;">
        <span style="display:inline-block;width:28px;height:1px;background:#2D3748;"></span>Service Overview
      </p>
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.7rem,3vw,2.2rem);font-weight:900;color:#1A202C;line-height:1.2;margin:0 0 18px;">What is Canada Certificate Attestation?</h2>
      <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:14px;">
        Canada certificate attestation is required when documents issued in Canada need legal acceptance in the UAE. The UAE authorities ask for this process to confirm that the document is genuine and issued by the correct authority in Canada. This applies to education, personal, and commercial documents.
      </p>
      <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:14px;">
        With 25+ years of experience, IndexAUH follows the correct embassy and MOFA steps to complete Canada attestation without delays. Our experts are ready to guide you from document review to final MOFA approval.
      </p>
      <div style="background:#F0FFFE;border:1px solid #B2F5EA;border-radius:12px;padding:18px;">
        <h3 style="color:#1A202C;font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 6px;">Key Insight — No Apostille for Canada</h3>
        <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">
          Canada is not part of the Hague Convention, so apostille is not applicable. Canada document attestation follows a specific legalization process involving Canadian authorities, the Canada UAE Embassy, and final MOFA approval in the UAE.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div style="position:relative;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);">
        <img src="/images/canada-flag.avif" alt="Canada document attestation UAE" style="width:100%;height:420px;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
        <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,transparent 50%,rgba(26,32,44,0.72) 100%);"></div>
        <div style="position:absolute;bottom:20px;left:20px;right:20px;">
          <p style="color:#fff;font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:800;margin:0 0 4px;">Notarization · Global Affairs · UAE Embassy · MOFA</p>
          <p style="color:#B2F5EA;font-size:0.75rem;margin:0;">Complete Canada attestation handled end-to-end</p>
        </div>
        <div style="position:absolute;bottom:80px;left:-14px;background:#2D3748;color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:10px;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
          25+ Years Experience
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ════ WHY REQUIRED ════ -->
<section style="background:#F8FAFF;padding:76px 24px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(45,55,72,0.02) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(45,55,72,0.02) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:40px 40px;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;"></div>

  <div class="sec-inner" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:44px;">
      <p style="color:#2D3748;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:0.75rem;margin-bottom:8px;">Key Situations</p>
      <h2 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:900;color:#1A202C;margin:0 0 14px;">Why Canada Certificate Attestation is Required in UAE?</h2>
      <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;">
        Canadian documents may be required in the UAE for employment, higher education, family sponsorship, licensing, immigration, or business activities. UAE authorities request attested documents to confirm legal authenticity before acceptance.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="three-col" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px;">
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #eef0f6;border-radius:16px;padding:28px;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:18px;">
          <span style="font-size:1.5rem;">🎓</span>
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:#1A202C;margin:0;">Educational Certificates</h3>
        </div>
       <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:9px;">
  {educationalNeeded.map(item => (
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;font-size:0.9rem;color:#4B5563;">
      <span style="color:#38B2AC;font-weight:bold;flex-shrink:0;">→</span><span set:html={item}></span>
    </div>
  ))}
</div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #eef0f6;border-radius:16px;padding:28px;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:18px;">
          <span style="font-size:1.5rem;">👤</span>
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:#1A202C;margin:0;">Personal Certificates</h3>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:9px;">
          {personalNeeded.map(item => (
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;font-size:0.9rem;color:#4B5563;">
              <span style="color:#38B2AC;font-weight:bold;flex-shrink:0;">→</span>{item}
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #eef0f6;border-radius:16px;padding:28px;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:18px;">
          <span style="font-size:1.5rem;">⚖️</span>
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:#1A202C;margin:0;">Commercial Documents</h3>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:9px;">
  {commercialNeeded.map(item => (
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;font-size:0.9rem;color:#4B5563;">
      <span style="color:#38B2AC;font-weight:bold;flex-shrink:0;">→</span><span set:html={item}></span>
    </div>
  ))}
</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ════ DOCUMENT TYPES ════ -->
<DocumentCoverage
  title="Our Canadian Document Attestation Services"
  description="We handle attestation for a wide range of document categories. Our team reviews everything carefully before submission to keep your documents compliant with UAE legalization requirements."
  imageSrc="/images/img-1.webp"
  imageAlt="Document types for Canada attestation"
  docTypes={docTypes}
  country="canada"
/>

<!-- ════ PROCESS STEPS ════ -->
<section style="background:#F0FFFE;padding:76px 24px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(45,55,72,0.02) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(45,55,72,0.02) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:44px 44px;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;"></div>

  <div class="sec-inner" style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div style="position:relative;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);margin-bottom:52px;">
      <img src="/images/img-7.webp" alt="Canada attestation process steps" style="width:100%;height:240px;object-fit:cover;object-position:center 35%;display:block;" />
      <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(26,32,44,0.88) 0%,rgba(26,32,44,0.5) 55%,transparent 100%);"></div>
      <div style="position:absolute;top:50%;left:40px;transform:translateY(-50%);">
        <p style="color:#38B2AC;font-weight:700;font-size:0.75rem;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 6px;">Step-by-Step</p>
        <h2 style="color:#fff;font-size:clamp(1.4rem,2.5vw,2rem);font-weight:900;margin:0;max-width:500px;line-height:1.25;">Procedure for Canadian Certificate Attestation</h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Standard Process -->
    <div class="split-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:40px;margin-bottom:40px;">
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:800;color:#1A202C;margin:0 0 18px;padding-left:14px;border-left:3px solid #38B2AC;">Standard Legalization Process</h3>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;">
          {standardSteps.map(s => (
  <div class="step-card">
    <div style="width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:10px;background:#2D3748;color:#38B2AC;font-weight:900;font-size:1rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">{s.step}</div>
    <div>
      <p style="font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:700;color:#1A202C;margin:0 0 4px;" set:html={s.title}></p>
      <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">{s.desc}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
))}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:28px;">
        <!-- Diploma -->
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:800;color:#1A202C;margin:0 0 14px;padding-left:14px;border-left:3px solid #38B2AC;">Canadian Diploma Certificate Attestation</h3>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;">
            {diplomaSteps.map(s => (
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #eef0f6;border-radius:12px;padding:12px 16px;">
    <div style="width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:8px;background:#2D3748;color:#38B2AC;font-weight:900;font-size:0.8rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">{s.step}</div>
    <div>
      <p style="font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:700;color:#1A202C;margin:0 0 2px;" set:html={s.title}></p>
      <p style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.5;margin:0;">{s.desc}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
))}

          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Degree -->
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:800;color:#1A202C;margin:0 0 14px;padding-left:14px;border-left:3px solid #38B2AC;">Degree Attestation Canada Procedure</h3>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;">
{degreeSteps.map(s => (
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #eef0f6;border-radius:12px;padding:12px 16px;">
    <div style="width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:8px;background:#2D3748;color:#38B2AC;font-weight:900;font-size:0.8rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">{s.step}</div>
    <div>
      <p style="font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:700;color:#1A202C;margin:0 0 2px;" set:html={s.title}></p>
      <p style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.5;margin:0;">{s.desc}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Auth vs Apostille -->
    <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #B2F5EA;border-radius:16px;padding:28px;">
      <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:#1A202C;margin:0 0 12px;">Canada Authentication vs Apostille</h3>
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">Many applicants mistakenly believe Canadian documents only need an apostille. However, Canadian documents for UAE use generally follow an authentication and legalization process instead. Submitting incomplete legalization can result in document rejection in the UAE. This usually involves:</p>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:10px;">
        {authSteps.map(s => (
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:#F0FFFE;border:1px solid #B2F5EA;border-radius:10px;padding:12px 16px;">
            <span style="color:#38B2AC;font-weight:bold;flex-shrink:0;">→</span>
            <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#374151;margin:0;font-weight:500;">{s}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
